cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with salient object detection in images. The use of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN) also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The use of hyperspectral imaging systems suggests that it could also belong to the information retrieval (cs.IR) category. Finally, the use of saliency maps suggests that it could belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) category.
